variables.name: ERROR_UNKNOWN
variables.comment: Unknown error code.

variables.name: ERROR_OTHER
variables.comment: Error code for other errors

variables.name: ERROR_RUNTIME
variables.comment: Error code for runtime errors

variables.name: ERROR_IO_NETWORK_UNAVAILABLE
variables.comment: Error code for lack of network connectivity while trying to access a network resource

variables.name: ERROR_IO_NETWORK_CONNECTION_FAILED
variables.comment: Error code for a failure while establishing a network connection

variables.name: ERROR_IO_BAD_HTTP_STATUS
variables.comment: Error code for an HTTP server returning an unexpected HTTP response status code

variables.name: ERROR_IO_DNS_FAILED
variables.comment: Error code for failing to resolve a hostname

variables.name: ERROR_IO_CONNECTION_TIMEOUT
variables.comment:
* Error code for a network timeout, meaning the server is taking too long to fulfill
     * a request

variables.name: ERROR_IO_CONNECTION_CLOSED
variables.comment: Error code for an existing network connection being unexpectedly closed

variables.name: ERROR_IO_OTHER
variables.comment: Error code for other Input/Output errors

variables.name: ERROR_PARSING_MANIFEST_MALFORMED
variables.comment: Error code for a parsing error associated to a media manifest

variables.name: ERROR_PARSING_CONTAINER_MALFORMED
variables.comment: Error code for a parsing error associated to a media container format bitstream

variables.name: ERROR_PARSING_OTHER
variables.comment: Error code for other media parsing errors

variables.name: ERROR_DECODER_INIT_FAILED
variables.comment: Error code for a decoder initialization failure

variables.name: ERROR_DECODING_FAILED
variables.comment: Error code for a failure while trying to decode media samples

variables.name: ERROR_DECODING_FORMAT_EXCEEDS_CAPABILITIES
variables.comment: * Error code for trying to decode content whose format exceeds the capabilities of the device.

variables.name: ERROR_DECODING_OTHER
variables.comment: Error code for other decoding errors

variables.name: ERROR_AUDIO_TRACK_INIT_FAILED
variables.comment: Error code for an AudioTrack initialization failure

variables.name: ERROR_AUDIO_TRACK_WRITE_FAILED
variables.comment: Error code for an AudioTrack write operation failure

variables.name: ERROR_AUDIO_TRACK_OTHER
variables.comment: Error code for other AudioTrack errors

variables.name: ERROR_PLAYER_REMOTE
variables.comment: Error code for an unidentified error in a remote controller or player

variables.name: ERROR_PLAYER_BEHIND_LIVE_WINDOW
variables.comment:
* Error code for the loading position falling behind the sliding window of available live
     * content.

variables.name: ERROR_PLAYER_OTHER
variables.comment: Error code for other player errors

variables.name: ERROR_DRM_SCHEME_UNSUPPORTED
variables.comment: Error code for a chosen DRM protection scheme not being supported by the device

variables.name: ERROR_DRM_PROVISIONING_FAILED
variables.comment: Error code for a failure while provisioning the device

variables.name: ERROR_DRM_LICENSE_ACQUISITION_FAILED
variables.comment: Error code for a failure while trying to obtain a license

variables.name: ERROR_DRM_DISALLOWED_OPERATION
variables.comment: Error code an operation being disallowed by a license policy

variables.name: ERROR_DRM_SYSTEM_ERROR
variables.comment: Error code for an error in the DRM system

variables.name: ERROR_DRM_CONTENT_ERROR
variables.comment: Error code for attempting to play incompatible DRM-protected content

variables.name: ERROR_DRM_DEVICE_REVOKED
variables.comment: Error code for the device having revoked DRM privileges

variables.name: ERROR_DRM_OTHER
variables.comment: Error code for other DRM errors

variables.name: ERROR_IO_FILE_NOT_FOUND
variables.comment: Error code for a non-existent file

variables.name: ERROR_IO_NO_PERMISSION
variables.comment:
* Error code for lack of permission to perform an IO operation, for example, lack of permission
     * to access internet or external storage.

variables.name: ERROR_PARSING_MANIFEST_UNSUPPORTED
variables.comment: Error code for an unsupported feature in a media manifest

variables.name: ERROR_PARSING_CONTAINER_UNSUPPORTED
variables.comment:
* Error code for attempting to extract a file with an unsupported media container format, or an
     * unsupported media container feature

variables.name: ERROR_DECODING_FORMAT_UNSUPPORTED
variables.comment: Error code for trying to decode content whose format is not supported
